324
00:13:09,320 --> 00:13:10,660
a and b are just letters.

325
00:13:10,660 --> 00:13:11,840
I can use them any way I want.

326
00:13:12,000 --> 00:13:14,040
m times a equals b.

327
00:13:18,900 --> 00:13:22,290
I'm interested in the component

328
00:13:22,290 --> 00:13:25,680
of b along the axis i.

329
00:13:25,920 --> 00:13:28,840
By that I mean these objects over here,

330
00:13:28,840 --> 00:13:29,520
the alphas,

