00:14:28,490 --> 00:14:29,940
to rewrite things in terms of components?

354
00:14:30,620 --> 00:14:32,920
I want to rewrite everything in terms of components

355
00:14:32,920 --> 00:14:34,280
so they actually become

356
00:14:35,980 --> 00:14:37,980
arithmetical operations that you can do.

357
00:14:38,939 --> 00:14:39,540
Well,

358
00:14:39,540 --> 00:14:42,520
here's where we use this trick.

359
00:14:43,720 --> 00:14:45,620
Now whenever you see a vector a,

