00:15:29,840 --> 00:15:31,420
go up to the top again,

379
00:15:32,720 --> 00:15:35,360
that's just alpha j.

380
00:15:37,500 --> 00:15:38,060
So,

381
00:15:38,060 --> 00:15:39,680
we now have a formula

