383
00:15:42,980 --> 00:15:46,760
This is i m j.

384
00:15:47,040 --> 00:15:48,320
I'll get to this in a minute,

385
00:15:48,320 --> 00:15:49,160
but it's a number.

386
00:15:49,740 --> 00:15:51,420
Inner products are numbers.

