00:17:19,060 --> 00:17:21,579
the collection of m i j's,

422
00:17:21,660 --> 00:17:24,079
and somebody hands you a vector

423
00:17:24,079 --> 00:17:25,720
in the form of its components,

424
00:17:26,000 --> 00:17:29,280
you can then start sweeping through it

425
00:17:29,900 --> 00:17:32,180
and calculating what the components

