00:17:41,300 --> 00:17:42,720
It's a square matrix.

430
00:17:43,440 --> 00:17:45,980
If the dimensionality of the space is n,

431
00:17:46,280 --> 00:17:52,120
then m is an n by n matrix.

432
00:17:52,460 --> 00:17:53,800
A square matrix.

433
00:17:54,560 --> 00:17:55,920
It's a square matrix,

434
00:17:55,920 --> 00:17:56,140
and it's a square matrix.

435
00:17:56,820 --> 00:17:59,500
Alpha can be regarded as a column.

436
00:18:00,800 --> 00:18:02,700
Alpha can be regarded as a column,

