00:18:45,400 --> 00:18:46,740
m two one,

458
00:18:46,740 --> 00:18:48,080
m two two,

459
00:18:48,260 --> 00:18:49,020
dot dot dot,

460
00:18:49,020 --> 00:18:50,120
dot dot dot dot dot dot.

461
00:18:51,520 --> 00:18:53,520
It's just an array that exhibits

462
00:18:53,520 --> 00:18:55,200
the matrix elements,

